chess.domain.pieces

Class King

  • java.lang.Object
    • chess.domain.pieces.Piece
      • chess.domain.pieces.King

  • public class King
extends Piece
    This class corresponds physical king-piece thus only containing knowledge of it's place and whether or not is has been moved. This class also offers a method to clone this king.

    sami
